      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1773640143639,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. YAML file describing the configuration\n2. Post Req the configuration file to the API server\n3. request will be authenticated & authorized\n4. application definition will be persisted in the cluster store etcd\n5. application’s containers will be scheduled to nodes ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. YAML file describing the configuration\n2. Post Req the configuration file to the API server\n3. request will be authenticated & authorized\n4. application definition will be persisted in the cluster store etcd\n5. application’s containers will be scheduled to nodes ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YbeDP6r4Ks7s2jVv7NfhQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2200,
      "y": 5540,
      "width": 935,
      "height": 100,
